External knowledge: 
- The state of an issue can change multiple times (e.g., from 'open' to 'closed' and then back to 'open');
- The total time spent on an issue is calculated by summing up all intervals between these state changes;
- The query assumes that an issue is being worked on when it is in the 'open' state and not when it is in the 'closed' state.
